{"title":"江之旅（二首）","authors":["杨山"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":11,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"江之旅（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹过峡江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的状态都发生变化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静　变为动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山也动了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风暖暖的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帆是传递信息的使者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悠长的号子颤动轻音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峡谷回应"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸上的树叶也翩翩起舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江面骤然加宽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船桅上的旗迎风飘举"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是现实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——船长说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必做恶梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在白天　在峡江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上晨日礼赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与夜奋力搏斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜红的旭日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从澎湃的浪中跳出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲吻年轻的水手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上遂有清亮的赞歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥远的地平线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于看到了太阳——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它以光焰廓清宇宙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江水里滚动着千万个火球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你曾被埋葬过的太阳呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你新鲜的热烈的太阳呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这万千火红的心的集合体呵"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}